==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
:tĕk-tŏn'ĭks

=== Noun ===

#'''Tectonics''' is the study of large-scale structural features of the Earth.
#A specialized branch of [[geology]] that deals with [[crust]]al [[plate]]s and their movements.

=== Adjective ===
#A '''tectonic plate''' is such a crustal feature. In this usage, ''tectonic'' becomes an adjective that implies a ''large'' plate, as opposed to a localized phenomenon.